203
00:13:15.050 --> 00:13:17.190
Hyun Soo, kami akan makan dengan Pak Park.

204
00:13:17.190 --> 00:13:18.290
Tolong carikan restoran bagus.

205
00:13:18.920 --> 00:13:19.960
Apa?

206
00:13:22.290 --> 00:13:24.259
Dialah yang membantu

207
